Step : 1
Create a script file  :           nano endpoint.sh

Paste the following into it:

#!/bin/bash

domain="target.com"

waybackurls "$domain" > wayback.txt
gau "$domain" >> wayback.txt

cat wayback.txt | sort -u > all_urls.txt

gf xss < all_urls.txt > xss.txt
gf sqli < all_urls.txt > sqli.txt
gf ssrf < all_urls.txt > ssrf.txt
gf idor < all_urls.txt > idor.txt



 Step 2: Make the Script Executable
 chmod +x endpoint_discovery.sh

Step : 3 Run
./endpoint.sh
